  "detailed_description": "<h1>Official FAQ</h1><p></p><br><h1>Official Discord Server</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/32088dccdc1d921b7b713e0bc06b6e8b.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=338 /></span>The Gates of Armantia Have Opened</h2></i>Welcome to the world of <strong><i>Second Wave</i></strong>, where the battle for supremacy is about to begin! Get ready to dive headfirst into a world that combines the best elements of competitive team-based shooters into an exhilarating gaming experience unlike any other!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/3a4a8eb64564b85e604ff72dc0a2d8d4.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/2e8dfb20aa3c6e4d62d6b32ed481555f.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/03a254635edad0bf7ed96fac07248c28.poster.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/03a254635edad0bf7ed96fac07248c28.webm?t=1718999303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/03a254635edad0bf7ed96fac07248c28.mp4?t=1718999303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Unlock the Hidden Mysteries</h2></i>Explore the history of Armantia and the lore surrounding Second Wave with our 400,000-word novel. Discover the full mystery of the Arcane Stone through the stories you'll unveil from in-game characters and even items that you may not consider to be significant.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/3a4a8eb64564b85e604ff72dc0a2d8d4.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/21dc5f02adb0dde6b861bb900137d172.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/9f5232223b55715ee7f241d18e1839b8.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=230 /></span>Intense PURE ACTION Combat</h2></i>Whether you're a fan of the tough-as-nails tank, the fearless warrior, the cunning ranged dealer, the mystical mage, the stealthy assassin, or the ever-reliable support, we have the perfect character for your style. Each hero is ready for battle, and some even have the ability to switch roles mid-game. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/3a4a8eb64564b85e604ff72dc0a2d8d4.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/eb9a0ee24d2babc657964e87b70f530d.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/de640caf6831749d3e88babf47f23ab7.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=192 /></span>Immersive Action Packed 6vs6 Multiplayer</h2></i>In Trestyn, a city with a towering energy core at its center, two teams battle for control of the core. Fight to the last breath to claim the core and wield the power of the arcane stone. In this 6 vs 6 mode, earn 1000 points by capturing locations or killing the roaming monsters.<br><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/441ebb5cbf476d283b3b839a2f865b61.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=192 /></span>The Ultimate 4vs4vs4 Experience</h2></i>Experience the unique challenge of three teams competing for the Arcane Stone hidden in the Red Circus. In this 4 vs 4 vs 4 mode, you must reach 1500 points by defeating the other two teams or capturing the two control points.<br><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/c7c75f5d12c1676835d10eff50b1473a.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=192 /></span>Rally Your Allies For This Legendary 3vs3vs3vs3 Challenge</h2></i>Engage in a race to capture the Arcane Stones as you battle three other teams for control of the stones. Rally your allies in this 3 vs 3 vs 3 vs 3 mode and collect 24 or more Arcane Stones and hold onto them for as long as possible to claim victory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/3a4a8eb64564b85e604ff72dc0a2d8d4.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/f21c1e5b760b2151f85e372a0370866e.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/c8abe61c98da0dc5a86382238f892a23.poster.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/c8abe61c98da0dc5a86382238f892a23.webm?t=1718999303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/c8abe61c98da0dc5a86382238f892a23.mp4?t=1718999303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Dominate Your Foes with Style</h2></i><strong><i>Second Wave</i></strong> offers a cosmetic-only store where players can purchase unique skins, effects, and voice lines for the characters in the game. Challengers Games is committed to providing a fair and balanced game with <strong><u>No Pay to Win</u></strong>.",
