s by capturing locations or killing the roaming monsters.<br><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/441ebb5cbf476d283b3b839a2f865b61.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=192 /></span>The Ultimate 4vs4vs4 Experience</h2></i>Experience the unique challenge of three teams competing for the Arcane Stone hidden in the Red Circus. In this 4 vs 4 vs 4 mode, you must reach 1500 points by defeating the other two teams or capturing the two control points.<br><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/c7c75f5d12c1676835d10eff50b1473a.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=192 /></span>Rally Your Allies For This Legendary 3vs3vs3vs3 Challenge</h2></i>Engage in a race to capture the Arcane Stones as you battle three other teams for control of the stones. Rally your allies in this 3 vs 3 vs 3 vs 3 mode and collect 24 or more Arcane Stones and hold onto them for as long as possible to claim victory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/3a4a8eb64564b85e604ff72dc0a2d8d4.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/f21c1e5b760b2151f85e372a0370866e.webp?t=1718999303\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/c8abe61c98da0dc5a86382238f892a23.poster.avif?t=1718999303\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337510/extras/c8abe61c98da0dc5a863